data.description:
DON'T PASS THIS UP! SELLER IS MOTIVATED and is offering a Seller's Concession. 

This Carothers Executive home is a 4 bedroom 2 bathroom beautiful house that sits on a little over 1/4 of an acre. As you walk in, you're greeted with an entertainer's dream coupled with an open concept for the Kitchen, Dining Room, and Living Room, all waiting for your company to arrive.
 In the living room it has a wood burning fireplace. The Kitchen has granite countertops with plenty of cabinet space and a walk-in pantry. As you walk into the Master Bedroom, you will find the DREAM Master Bathroom to impress anyone. This master bathroom has a garden tub, his/hers sinks, walk-in closets, vanities, and showers!
